name: Zooplankton community and pelagic copepods in Tudor creek (Mombasa, Kenya) between 1984 and 1987
description: List of zooplankton taxa and copepoda species for 5 stations in Tudorcreek sampled between December 1984 and December 1987. The data were digitizedby VLIZ from theoriginal report: Okemwa, E. (1990). A studyof the pelagic copepods (Copepoda; Crustacea) in a tropicalmarine creek Tudor, Mombasa,Kenya, with a special reference to their community structure, biomass and productivity. PhD Thesis. VUB: Brussel. 225 pp.
